<u>Research Presentation Sessions&nbsp;</u></div>
<ul style=3D"text-align:left; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; background=
-color:rgb(255,255,255)">
<li style=3D"font-family:Aptos,Aptos_EmbeddedFont,Aptos_MSFontService,Calib=
ri,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:12pt; color:black; direction:ltr; list-s=
tyle-position:initial; list-style-type:disc">
<div class=3D"x_elementToProof" role=3D"presentation" style=3D"direction:lt=
r; line-height:1.38; margin:0px">
<span style=3D"text-transform:none">Moderators, as well as presenters and p=
anelists, should
<b>arrive in the room of your session at least</b>&nbsp;</span><span style=
=3D"font-weight:700; text-transform:none">5 minutes before the session=92s =
start time.</span></div>
</li><li style=3D"font-family:Aptos,Aptos_EmbeddedFont,Aptos_MSFontService,=
Calibri,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:12pt; color:black; direction:ltr; l=
ist-style-position:initial; list-style-type:disc">
<div class=3D"x_elementToProof" role=3D"presentation" style=3D"direction:lt=
r; line-height:1.38; margin:0px">
<span style=3D"text-transform:none">The flow for </span><span style=3D"font=
-weight:700; text-transform:none">Research Presentations</span><span style=
=3D"text-transform:none">&nbsp;is as follows:</span></div>
</li><ul style=3D"margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px">
<li style=3D"font-family:Aptos,Aptos_EmbeddedFont,Aptos_MSFontService,Calib=
ri,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:12pt; color:black; direction:ltr; list-s=
tyle-position:initial; list-style-type:disc">
<div class=3D"x_elementToProof" role=3D"presentation" style=3D"direction:lt=
r; line-height:1.38; margin:0px">
<span style=3D"text-transform:none">Moderator will briefly introduce the se=
ssion including its topic and format.&nbsp;</span></div>
</li><li style=3D"font-family:Aptos,Aptos_EmbeddedFont,Aptos_MSFontService,=
Calibri,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:12pt; color:black; direction:ltr; l=
ist-style-position:initial; list-style-type:disc">
<div class=3D"x_elementToProof" role=3D"presentation" style=3D"direction:lt=
r; line-height:1.38; margin:0px">
<span style=3D"text-transform:none">Presenters&nbsp;will present their rese=
arch for </span>
<span style=3D"font-weight:700; text-transform:none">10 minutes each </span=
><span style=3D"text-transform:none">in the order designated on the Researc=
hers Meeting schedule. Please follow that order as some people move session=
 to session to see different presentations.
 &nbsp;The agenda can be located <a href=3D"https://urldefense.com/v3/__htt=
ps://hazards.colorado.edu/workshop/2026/researchers-meeting/translating-com=
plexity-assessment-models-and-markets-in-a-changing-climate__;!!JmPEgBY0HMs=
zNaDT!viinU1YZtl8Dd1A1_cUZqq3oYz3XvId_iKW4h8bb5ulKssBSnElq_h4M67zvT_9b_NQFL=
FCZ_BGCm34HPULK$" data-outlook-id=3D"dcdf86b5-e46a-415c-bd74-a812c0eb7278">
here</a>.&nbsp;</span></div>
</li><li style=3D"font-family:Aptos,Aptos_EmbeddedFont,Aptos_MSFontService,=
Calibri,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:12pt; color:black; direction:ltr; l=
ist-style-position:initial; list-style-type:disc">
<div class=3D"x_elementToProof" role=3D"presentation" style=3D"direction:lt=
r; line-height:1.38; margin:0px">
<span style=3D"text-transform:none">Questions will be held until after<i>&n=
bsp;</i>all presentations are complete.&nbsp;</span></div>
</li><li style=3D"font-family:Aptos,Aptos_EmbeddedFont,Aptos_MSFontService,=
Calibri,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:12pt; color:black; direction:ltr; l=
ist-style-position:initial; list-style-type:disc">
<div class=3D"x_elementToProof" role=3D"presentation" style=3D"direction:lt=
r; line-height:1.38; margin:0px">
<span style=3D"text-transform:none">After the research presentations, as th=
e moderator, I will turn to the audience for questions. In case the audienc=
e is initially quiet, I will have a question or two ready to go (but please=
 privilege the audience questions,
 first, to ensure engagement).&nbsp;</span></div>
</li><li style=3D"font-family:Aptos,Aptos_EmbeddedFont,Aptos_MSFontService,=
Calibri,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:12pt; color:black; direction:ltr; l=
ist-style-position:initial; list-style-type:disc">
<div class=3D"x_elementToProof" role=3D"presentation" style=3D"direction:lt=
r; line-height:1.38; margin:0px">
<span style=3D"text-transform:none">As I&nbsp;close the session, I will mak=
e sure to thank all the panelists, the student volunteer, and the audience =
members for their participation!&nbsp;</span></div>
</li></ul>
</ul>
<div style=3D"font-family:Aptos,Aptos_EmbeddedFont,Aptos_MSFontService,Cali=
bri,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:12pt; color:rgb(0,0,0)">
<span style=3D"text-transform:none">I look forward to seeing you all at the=
 session. Please feel free to reach out if you have any questions.</span></=
div>
<div style=3D"direction:ltr; font-family:Aptos,Aptos_EmbeddedFont,Aptos_MSF=
ontService,Calibri,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:12pt; color:rgb(0,0,0)">
<span style=3D"text-transform:none"><br>
</span></div>
<div style=3D"direction:ltr; font-family:Aptos,Aptos_EmbeddedFont,Aptos_MSF=
ontService,Calibri,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:12pt; color:rgb(0,0,0)">
<span style=3D"text-transform:none">Safe travels next week!&nbsp;</span></d=
iv>
<div style=3D"direction:ltr; font-family:Aptos,Aptos_EmbeddedFont,Aptos_MSF=
ontService,Calibri,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:12pt; color:rgb(0,0,0)">
<span style=3D"text-transform:none">Amy</span></div>
<div style=3D"direction:ltr; font-family:Aptos,Aptos_EmbeddedFont,Aptos_MSF=
ontService,Calibri,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:12pt; color:rgb(0,0,0)">
<span style=3D"text-transform:none"><br>
</span></div>
<div style=3D"direction:ltr; font-family:Aptos,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; =
